{
  "texts": [
    "We demonstrated the importance of incorporating an artifact detector in conjunction with a seizure detection framework to reduce the number of false alarms.",
    "In fact, using the artifact detector allowed for a 96% reduction in FP/h.",
    "The proposed framework also allows for multi-day continuous operation when executed on an ultra-lowpower device.",
    "In fact, by optimizing the implementation of the framework for a PULP platform, we demonstrated a power envelope of 26.1 mW and energy usage as low as 7.93 µ J per window feature extraction and classification.",
    "Our algorithms were primarily developed for standard EEGs with traditional electrodes."
  ]
}